message.body: Hello
Hello! How are you?
Hello. Better now that I've had my coffee :-)
Haha I bet! Is it morning by you?
No not actually. It is for.me though. What part of the US are you on?
Haha I'm in the midwest. Did you really just wake up? !
Yes from a nap. I work a lot so my weekends is my time to be lazy.
What do you do on your days off??
Ooh! Well, unfortunately I'm a student so I dont have any days off. I'm either at the library or work!
What about you? Do you have a full time job then?
Oh ok. Cool. What are you studying if you don't mind me asking?
Yes. I work for a mortgage co. And graphic design part time
I'm studying dynamics and mechanics of materials. I'm an engineering major. :)
Oh. Sounds boring :-)
You must love Math and Science
Hahaha as boring as any physics classes! Wow, two jobs?!?! How do you do it?
Well neither is very demanding. Not sure how I actually manage to do that, AND come home and cook. Lol.. but I do. Someone has to do it.
Oh, I do love math and science, I do! Ever since I was young, I wanted to become the next bill nye!
Wow, you cook? I love to bake and cook, too! I just made coffeecake this morning!
Lol... Yummie! Yes I have a boyfriend who loves to eat, and my nephew lives with me. So they eyeball me with the hungry eye when I get in. Smh...
Hahaha! Whats your favorite recipe?
Oh shoot if I had to pick one! It'll probably be my moms chili. I have so many though. What's yours?
Oh, chili sounds so good right now! Ive been on a steady college diet of pbj and oatmeal for so long! My favorite is italian stir fry! Ugh I love veggies!
Sounds good. Are you Italian?
Nope! Haha, german all the way. Italian stir fry is just veggies cooked in red wine vinegar, so good.
